cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CR 

The paper proposes a deep learning-based approach for item-based collaborative filtering, which is a popular technique in recommender systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves natural language processing techniques, which could place it in cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cybersecurity, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
